---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Return Policy | fashionCulture">
    <main>
        <section class="return-policy-section">
            <h1>Return Policy</h1>

            <div class="content-block">
                <p>
                    At fashionCulture, we are committed to ensuring your satisfaction with every purchase. If you are not entirely satisfied with your purchase, we are here to help. Please read our return policy carefully to understand our procedures and conditions for returning items.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Eligibility for Returns</h2>
                <p><strong>Timeframe:</strong> You have 30 days from the date of delivery to return any items.</p>
                <p><strong>Condition:</strong> Items must be unworn, unwashed, and in their original condition with all tags attached. Items that do not meet these criteria will not be eligible for return.</p>
                <p><strong>Non-returnable items:</strong> Certain items, such as underwear, swimwear, and sale items, are non-returnable unless they are defective or damaged.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Return Process</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Request a Return:</strong> Contact our customer support team at <a href="mailto:support@fashionCulture.com">support@fashionCulture.com</a> to request a return authorization. Please provide your order number and the reason for the return.</li>
                    <li><strong>Pack Your Items:</strong> Securely pack the items in their original packaging, if possible. Include the return authorization slip provided by our customer support team.</li>
                    <li><strong>Ship Your Return:</strong> Send the package to the return address provided by our customer support team. We recommend using a trackable shipping method to ensure your return reaches us safely.</li>
                    <li><strong>Processing Your Return:</strong> Once we receive your return, we will inspect the items to ensure they meet our return policy criteria. If approved, your refund will be processed within 5-7 business days. The refund will be issued to your original payment method.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Exchanges</h2>
                <p>We do not offer direct exchanges. If you need a different size, color, or item, please return the original item and place a new order.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Refunds</h2>
                <p><strong>Refund Method:</strong> Refunds will be issued to the original payment method used for the purchase.</p>
                <p><strong>Processing Time:</strong> Please allow 5-7 business days for the refund to appear in your account after it has been processed.</p>
                <p><strong>Shipping Costs:</strong> Original shipping costs are non-refundable. If your return is due to a defect or error on our part, we will cover the return shipping costs.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <style>
        main {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .return-policy-section {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #444;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }

        p, li {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .content-block {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        ol {
            list-style-type: decimal;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        strong {
            color: #000;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>
